Some of the famous snowfall places in Uttarakhand that can be easily reached from Delhi are Chopta,Tungnath, Chakrata, Pauri, Chamba, Nag Tibba, Mussoorie, 
Auli, Nainital, Dhanaulti, Munsiyari, Harsil etc.
